<div id="top" class="wrap clearfix four columns ">
  <div id="main-content" class="container clearfix">
    <div class="row">
	    <div class="twelve columns">
	      
	      <%= form_for @message do |f| %>
        	<h6>
        	  Simvla cultivates a premier and invite-based network of creative people to share their experiences and create a huge resource of the most diverse topics. We try to deliver the best content from up and coming as well as established creatives and pull it all together in one location, giving them custom tools to streamline their writing experience.
        	</h6>
          <h6>
            We provide our members with a clear and responsive front-end design, a fast and minimalistic content management system and all our effort in terms of pushing content to the world trough all the relevant channels available. All this baked with free, managed and super fast cloud hosting as well as a bunch of key features which will enrich their blogging experience.
          </h6>
          <h6>
            We're constantly looking for new creatives to join our community: If you are looking for a simple yet powerful blogging experience, look no more; fill in the form and you'll hear from us.
          </h6>
          <div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :name, "First Name" %>
            <%= f.text_field :name, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :lastname, "Last Name" %>
            <%= f.text_field :lastname, :class => "pane_input"%>        
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :email, "Email" %>
            <%= f.text_field :email, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :blog, "Blog / Website" %>
            <%= f.text_field :blog, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :twitter, "Twitter " %>
            <%= f.text_field :twitter, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :specialization, "What's your specialization?" %>
            <%= f.text_field :specialization, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
            <%= f.label :info, "Anything we should know?" %>
            <%= f.text_field :info, :class => "pane_input"%>
          </div>
          <div class="twelve columns">
             <p>
               <%= f.submit "send application", :class => "nice radius large white button" %>
            </p>
          </div>
          </div>

        <% end %>
	      
	      
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
    
